            <title>[LU-17479] Update lnetctl to allow cYAML to handle PyYAML format.</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-17479</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;cYAML is not forgiving for indentation style. If you generate a LNet YAML configuration file using PyYAML it currently will not work. Also YAML setup generated using libyaml directly will have the same issue.&#160; This work will allow our LNet tools to work with PyYAML.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>Any LNet setup.</environment>
